13:53.563 --> 13:57.267
♪ And if I mess it up
sometimes ♪

13:57.267 --> 14:00.570
♪ Nobody's perfect
You live and you learn it ♪

14:00.570 --> 14:04.174
♪ 'Cause everybody
makes mistakes ♪

14:04.174 --> 14:09.519
♪ Nobody's perfect
